
Sun, Sex and Surfing.
Embark on a journey with Lexi Tagget, Ally Styx, Alex Hale and Layla Redden ,as they travel with a group of friends to Ibiza for their Spring break. There they will learn who their true friends are and maybe the meanings of love. Follow these four  friends and learn their weaknesses and see if they each have someone in store for them. The truth is when lies, deception and double crossing are involved you can never know what's in store for these girls.